  <section id="Abishek">
    <h2>About Abishek</h2>
    <p><b>Name:</b> Abishek</p>

    <h3>Early Life</h3>
    <p>Abishek was born and raised in <b>Chennai</b> on <b>6th November 2006</b>, and he has lived his entire life in the city. 
    He studied at <b>SBOA JC</b> for all his schooling. From a young age, he was known for his <b>hyperactive and energetic personality</b>, 
    always eager to try out new activities and take part in everything around him. 
    Whether it was playing cricket, reading books, or simply running around with friends, Abishek was always full of life and enthusiasm.</p>

    <h3>Sports & Achievements</h3>
    <p>His extroverted nature allowed him to connect with many people, and he became well-liked among his peers. 
    Abishek’s love for sports was evident early on—he not only played cricket passionately but also represented the <b>Tamil Nadu state team</b>. 
    Additionally, he brought pride to his school by winning <b>two cluster-level championships in handball</b>, showcasing his talent and dedication in athletics.</p>

    <h3>Academics</h3>
    <p>Abishek’s academic journey has been filled with <b>ups and downs</b>. 
    Despite facing challenges at times, he always displayed the determination to overcome obstacles and keep moving forward. 
    His curiosity about technology grew stronger with time, and he developed a deep interest in <b>coding and computer science</b>. 
    This passion has guided his academic choices and future goals.</p>

    <h3>Future Aspirations</h3>
    <p>Looking ahead, Abishek aspires to <b>excel in coding</b> and strengthen his knowledge in computer science. 
    He is determined to carve out a successful career in the tech field, landing a role where he can apply his skills and continue to grow. 
    With his extroverted personality, sporting achievements, and resilience in academics, Abishek stands as a well-rounded individual prepared to take on the future with confidence.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Raghuveer Biography -->
  <section id="Raghuveer">
    <h2>About Raghuveer</h2>
    <p><b>Name:</b> Raghuveer</p>

    <h3>Early Life</h3>
    <p>Raghuveer was born on <b>1st August 2006</b> in <b>Chennai</b>. 
    His educational journey began at <b>Euro Kids</b> for playschool, followed by <b>Kola Perumal</b> for pre-KG. 
    From <b>LKG to 12th grade</b>, he studied at <b>DAV</b> for 14 years, a school that played a central role in shaping his personality, values, and academic foundation. 
    During his school years, Raghuveer built strong friendships and grew into an inquisitive and thoughtful individual.</p>

    <h3>Childhood Curiosity</h3>
    <p>From an early age, Raghuveer showed a love for <b>building and creating</b>. 
    Between the ages of 9 and 11, he was fascinated with <b>electronics and DIY toys</b>, spending hours experimenting with circuits and gadgets. 
    This innovative spark hinted at his future career interests and laid the foundation for his passion for engineering.</p>

    <h3>Passion for Football</h3>
    <p>As he grew older, Raghuveer’s interests shifted toward <b>football</b>. 
    Since 2018, he has been a devoted supporter of <b>Lionel Messi</b> and the <b>Manchester City Football Club</b>. 
    Football not only provided him with entertainment but also instilled values of <b>teamwork, discipline, and perseverance</b>. 
    Following the sport remains one of his favorite pastimes, and he continues to be inspired by his idols.</p>

    <h3>Academics & College</h3>
    <p>In his <b>10th grade</b>, Raghuveer decided to pursue <b>engineering</b> and began preparing for JEE. 
    Although he underestimated the intense competition at first, his perseverance and adaptability ensured his success in clearing the <b>VITEEE exam</b>. 
    Today, he is pursuing a degree in <b>Computer Science at VIT Chennai</b>, aligning perfectly with his long-standing interest in technology and problem-solving.</p>

    <h3>Life at VIT</h3>
    <p>His time at VIT has been transformative. 
    Beyond academics, he learned how to <b>socialize and communicate</b> with students from diverse backgrounds across India. 
    He even picked up conversational Hindi, a skill that helped him connect with a wider group of peers. 
    These experiences broadened his perspective on life and gave him valuable exposure to different cultures and ideas.</p>

    <h3>Future Aspirations</h3>
    <p>Raghuveer dreams of becoming a <b>successful software engineer</b> and contributing to impactful projects in the tech industry. 
    He envisions himself working on innovative solutions while balancing his passion for football and creativity. 
    His journey from building electronic toys to coding projects in college shows his resilience, adaptability, and ambition. 
    With his drive and determination, Raghuveer is well-prepared to shape a promising future for himself.</p>
  </section>

